    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but small steps dont actually fix anything. the interest is just growing every single day. it's like a hole that gets deeper the more i try to climb out. i've tried everything and nothing works. it's just a constant weight on my chest. it feels like i'm just existing to pay for mistakes i cant even fix anymore.",
      "source": "evaluator"
